which constructs a tetrahedron from four points.
<P>

</TD></TR>
        <TR><TD><BR></TD></TR>
        <TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=100% NOWRAP COLSPAN=2>
        <I><NOBR>
